title: Episode 358: Student of the Bedroom (Feat. Rubi Rose)
itunes:title: Episode 358: Student of the Bedroom (Feat. Rubi Rose)
description:
Rapper/Model, Rubi Rose joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her latest single "Wifey." The ladies discuss fighting with your partner while on vacations, being with men secure enough to handle your OnlyFans hustle, cheating to get back at your partner, and much more. Rubi even opens up about how she just recently learned how to orgasm! We can't wait for Rubi to come back and hand in her homework. Enjoy!
